  "title": "HR Business Partner",
  "description": "<p><strong>HR Business Partner - Pioneer Sector - MNC Industrial Packaging</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Manage payroll, CPF, and statutory HR matters</li><li>Administer work permits, medicals, insurance, and MOM compliance</li><li>Support recruitment, onboarding, exits, and re-employment</li><li>Maintain HRIS, personnel files, and HR documentation</li><li>Prepare HR reports and surveys</li><li>Coordinate internships and employee engagement initiatives</li><li>Report to HR Manager</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least Diploma in HR</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office suite of applications.</li><li>Knowledge in managing foreign workers.</li><li>Knowledge of payroll processing.</li><li>Employment Laws and regulations.</li><li>Require minimum 3 years experience</li><li>Must have payroll experience  and CPF related matter</li></ul><p><strong>Working hour:</strong></p><p>Mon to Fri 8am - 5pm</p><p>For interested applicants, kindly send your resume in Word/PDF format to include the following in your resume including:</p><p>1. Current Salary</p><p>2. Expected Salary</p><p>3. Availability</p><p>4. Reason for leaving</p><p></p><p>Thank you for your application and we regret that only shortlisted applicants will be notified</p><p>By submitting any application or resume to us, you will be deemed to have agreed & consented to us collecting, using, retaining & disclosing your personal information to prospective employers with the services provided by us.</p><p>Nguyen Thi Doan | R23116355</p><p>RRecruiter Pte. Ltd. | 18C9514</p><p></p>",
